body:
Dear {project_manager},

Attached is the Resource Utilisation graph for {project_name} as of {date}.

This report highlights resource loading across the project schedule. Periods of over-allocation (usage exceeding 100%) are shown in a distinct colour and may require immediate attention — consider levelling, splitting, or re-assigning tasks as appropriate.

Summary:
  - View exported: {view_name}
  - Date generated: {date}
  - Project: {project_name}

Please review and take action on any highlighted over-allocation periods.

Kind regards,
{project_manager}
